Add-on:             Splunk for Cisco Security
Last Modified:	    04/01/12
Splunk Version:	    4.3 or higher
Author:             Splunk

The Splunk for Cisco Security app provides reports and dashboards that give you visual insight into your data from Cisco devices including the Ironport Email Security Appliance, Ironport Web Security Appliance, Cisco Firewalls and the Cisco IPS. Splunk for Cisco Security reports on data that is generated by the following add-ons:
 * Splunk for Cisco Firewalls (FWSM, ASA or PIX)
 * Splunk for Cisco SDEE/IPS
 * Splunk for Cisco IronPort Web Security
 * Splunk for Cisco IronPort E-mail Security

##### What's New #####
