1.0.1 (05.22.11)
- Resolved issue (SOLN-949) that causes the map to fail on a Windows system when package extracted using Winzip

1.0.0 (03.07.11)
- Updated to provide compatibility with Splunk 4.2
- Updated to include a setup application

